            <title>[SOLR-6111] The &apos;deleteshard&apos; collection API should be able to delete a shard in &apos;construction&apos; state</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6111</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &apos;deleteshard&apos; doesn&apos;t delete shards in &apos;construction&apos; state. This makes it impossible to clean up a split gone wrong. It should be able to delete any shard which is not in active state.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
